   ---

   ADDITIONAL NOTICE — RESEARCH USE ONLY

   This package and the underlying Peptide Design Attestation (PDA)
   protocol are scoped to nonclinical research evaluation only.

   Successful verification of any vector proves only that the
   cryptographic chain of custody is internally consistent. It does NOT
   imply that any peptide design referenced is safe for human use,
   effective for any therapeutic indication, or compliant with any
   regulatory framework.

   Software status: EXPERIMENTAL. The verification harness and the
   verifier package are subject to change. The three published vectors
   and their PDA hashes are frozen at protocol V1 and will not change
   without a major version bump.
